text: Christophe Masike (born 5 June 1998) is a Zimbabwean cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut for Mid West Rhinos in the 2018–19 Stanbic Bank 20 Series on 15 March 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Zimbabwean cricketers Category:Mid West Rhinos cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
